<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pranav’s 21st Birthday Mega Giveaway: Claim Your Free iPhone!</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;800&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: #fff; text-align: center; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; padding: 20px; }
        .card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); padding: 40px; border-radius: 30px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37); max-width: 500px; width: 100%; }
        .avatar { width: 100px; height: 100px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 40px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
        h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.2; }
        p { font-size: 1rem; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .badge { background: #ff4757; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.8rem; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .btn { display: block; padding: 18px; background: #2ed573; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 15px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(46, 213, 115, 0.4); }
        .btn:active { transform: scale(0.95); }
        .timer { margin-top: 25px; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: #ffa502; }
        footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.7rem; opacity: 0.6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="badge">Limited 21st Birthday Edition</div>
        <div class="avatar">🎁</div>
        <h1>Pranav is giving away <br>FREE iPhone 16 Pro Max!</h1>
        <p>“I’m officially 21! To celebrate, I’m giving away 2100 iPhones to my friends and family. Click below to verify your address.”</p>
        
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ" class="btn">CLAIM MY iPHONE NOW</a>
        
        <div class="timer">
            Connecting to Secure Dispatch Server... <span id="timer">15</span>s
        </div>
        
        <footer>
            © 2026 Pranav Gupta Celebrations • Terms & Conditions Apply
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        let count = 15;
        setInterval(() => {
            count--;
            document.getElementById("timer").innerText = count;
            if (count <= 0) window.location.href = "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ";
        }, 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
